====================================
Get the index of an array:
---------------------
Wrong code:
  import java.util.Arrays;
  int[] inorder = {1, 2};
  int pos = Arrays.asList(inorder).indexOf(2);

Result:
  pos = -1; // This means it never occrurred.

Reason:
  the indexOf method returns the occurrence position of a character in a string. Our array is not a string...

Solution:
  write an iteration function yourself...
====================================
